-- Kenya Gets $55 Million Loan From World Bank to Combat AIDS, Malaria Deaths
-- B y   E r i c   O m b o k
-- 2010-12-15T05:46:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-15/kenya-gets-55-million-loan-from-world-bank-to-combat-aids-malaria-deaths.html
The World Bank approved a $55
million loan to fund treatments for AIDS and purchase mosquito
nets to prevent malaria, the Washington-based lender said in an
e-mailed statement late yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
